Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.91,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fnHYXuanSong 65S\fs60\pos(640,576)\bord3\blur4}賽因水鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:08.90,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnFZLanTingHei-DB-GBK\fs21\c&H060E1B&\3c&H6096AF&\bord2\pos(47,260)}身軀巨大的人{\c&H864E6F&}族{\c&H060E1B&}。持續旅行，並擁有漫{\c&H864E6F&}長{\c&H060E1B&}的生命。\N一般巨人{\c&H864E6F&}的{\c&H060E1B&}身高在10米左右，大的{\c&H864E6F&}可{\c&H060E1B&}達30米。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:11.99,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fnHYXuanSong 65S\fs60\pos(640,576)\bord3\blur4}托吉埃市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.98,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an7\fsp2\fnHYXuanSong 65S\fs45\bord3\blur4\c&H000000&\3c&HEEEEEE&\pos(97,406)}人類\N{\fs50}第十七卿：紅紙簽愛蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:28.37,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an7\fsp2\fnHYXuanSong 65S\fs45\bord3\blur4\c&H000000&\3c&HEEEEEE&\pos(143,280)}造人\N{\fs50}流浪的丘涅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.63,0:22:58.14,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,500)\an7\fsp2\fnHYXuanSong 65S\fs45\bord3\blur4\c&H000000&\3c&HEEEEEE&\pos(125,314)}人類\N{\fs50}柳之劍宗次朗
